      <title>在看跌信号的情况下</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-14/tesla-dip-buyers-face-a-treacherous-path-amid-bearish-signals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特斯拉公司（Tesla Inc.）在不到两个月的时间内就剥离了其价值的四分之一，总计约4000亿美元。然而，对于考虑潜入电动车制造商股票的投资者，华尔街有一条信息：买家当心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-14/tesla-dip-buyers-face-a-treacherous-path-amid-bearish-signals</guid>
