      <title>Hermès的销售跃升，随着豪华低迷期间的标签优于表现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-14/hermes-sales-jump-as-label-outperforms-during-luxury-slowdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当富裕的购物者在假期中抢购了昂贵的手袋，与奢侈品同行相比，富裕的购物者抢购了其昂贵的手袋，而富裕的购物者抢购了其昂贵的手袋，而Hermès的销量激增。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-14/hermes-sales-jump-as-label-outperforms-during-luxury-slowdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Feb 2025 07:01:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当特朗普关税承诺燃料避风港的需求时，黄金持续了记录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-14/gold-holds-near-record-as-trump-tariff-pledges-fuel-haven-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）对几个国家的互惠关税命令下，黄金在创纪录的高位上进行了第三天的交易，这增加了贸易和全球经济的不确定性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-14/gold-holds-near-record-as-trump-tariff-pledges-fuel-haven-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Feb 2025 00:09:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
